<subSubSection id="C36B651CFFEDC12C66ABFF6C640348F4" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BCE3697FFEDC12C66ABFF6C640348F4" blockId="120.[151,1436,152,503]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C66ABFF6C602149B0" bold="true" box="[151,267,153,179]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B66FFEDC12C6729FF6C609849B0" author="Simon, E." box="[277,434,153,179]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" pagination="381 - 668" refId="ref110864" refString="Simon, E. (1901) Histoire naturelle des Araignees. Tome Second. Deuxieme Edition. Roret, Paris, 288 pp. [pp. 381 - 668]" type="book chapter" year="1901">Simon (1901)</bibRefCitation>
listed this “species” together with 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C6577FF6C62EE49B0" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1850" box="[843,964,153,179]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C6577FF6C62EE49B0" box="[843,964,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Corythalia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[at that time sub 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C62AAFF6C640649B0" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1876" box="[1174,1324,153,179]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Habrocestum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C62AAFF6C640649B0" box="[1174,1324,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Habrocestum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C6303FF6C601849D4" authority="Simon (1888)" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1888" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="locuples">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C6303FF6C64B649B0" box="[1343,1436,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">locuples</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B66FFEDC12C66ABFF48601849D4" author="Simon, E." box="[151,306,189,215]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" pagination="203 - 216" refId="ref110818" refString="Simon, E. (1888) Etudes arachnologiques. 21 e Memoire. XXIX. Descriptions d'especes et de genres nouveaux de l'Amerique centrale et des Antilles. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, Seires 6, 8, 203 - 216." type="journal article" year="1888">Simon (1888)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(see below), so it once must have been collected in the same locality as 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C626BFF4865FF49D4" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1888" box="[1111,1237,189,215]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="locuples">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C626BFF4865FF49D4" box="[1111,1237,189,215]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">C. locuples</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingRegion id="49B5F875FFEDC12C62DFFF4864B249D4" box="[1251,1432,189,215]" country="Dominican Republic" name="Santo Domingo" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Santo Domingo</collectingRegion>
, Hispaniola). A description does neither exist under the genus name 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C65A9FF14650149F8" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1876" box="[917,1067,225,251]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Habrocestum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C65A9FF14650149F8" box="[917,1067,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Habrocestum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
nor under 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C6294FF14640B49F8" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1850" box="[1192,1313,225,251]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C6294FF14640B49F8" box="[1192,1313,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Corythalia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Additionally, (a) 
<typeStatus id="54CA8835FFEDC12C66CEFEF0600C481C" box="[242,294,261,287]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">type</typeStatus>
(s) was/were never designated and deposited. Accordingly, a characterisation of 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C629CFEF06429481C" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[1184,1283,261,287]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="major">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C629CFEF06429481C" box="[1184,1283,261,287]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">C. major</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is impossible and the invalid status as a 
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C67FBFEDF634C4840" box="[455,614,297,323]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">nomen nudum</emphasis>
is justified. In the context of the first description of 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C62FCFEDC64024840" authorityName="Bryant" authorityYear="1950" box="[1216,1320,297,323]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Anasaitis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C62FCFEDC64024840" box="[1216,1320,297,323]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Anasaitis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[formerly temporarily in 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C6700FEB860F84864" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1876" box="[316,466,333,359]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Habrocestum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C6700FEB860F84864" box="[316,466,333,359]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Habrocestum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C643AFEB863554864" authorityName="C. L. Koch" authorityYear="1850" box="[518,639,333,359]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C643AFEB863554864" box="[518,639,333,359]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">Corythalia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C64B3FEB862A64864" authority="Simon (1888)" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1888" box="[655,908,333,359]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="locuples">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C64B3FEB863C64864" box="[655,748,333,359]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">locuples</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B66FFEDC12C64CEFEB862A64864" author="Simon, E." box="[754,908,333,359]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" pagination="203 - 216" refId="ref110818" refString="Simon, E. (1888) Etudes arachnologiques. 21 e Memoire. XXIX. Descriptions d'especes et de genres nouveaux de l'Amerique centrale et des Antilles. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, Seires 6, 8, 203 - 216." type="journal article" year="1888">Simon (1888)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
seemingly mentioned a specimen varying from the 
<typeStatus id="54CA8835FFEDC12C66F8FE8461DE4888" box="[196,244,369,395]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C714D14FFEDC12C671DFE87608E4888" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1888" box="[289,420,369,395]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Corythalia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="locuples">
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C671DFE87608E4888" box="[289,420,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">H. locuples</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and stated: “... 
<emphasis id="B905EA85FFEDC12C6464FE87645E4888" box="[600,1396,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">prope oculos squamulis majoribus laetissime purpureo-aureis vestita</emphasis>
...”. However, he did not list it officially as variant or subspecies with an explicit heading and an explicit description. A few years later 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE04B66FFEDC12C677FFE4C60F448D0" author="Simon, E." box="[323,478,441,467]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121" pagination="381 - 668" refId="ref110864" refString="Simon, E. (1901) Histoire naturelle des Araignees. Tome Second. Deuxieme Edition. Roret, Paris, 288 pp. [pp. 381 - 668]" type="book chapter" year="1901">Simon (1901)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned the species name, so, it is well imaginable that he had planned to describe a species with this name (including designation and deposition of a 
<typeStatus id="54CA8835FFEDC12C65B1FE28629548F4" box="[909,959,477,503]" pageId="120" pageNumber="121">type</typeStatus>
) subsequently, but he never did.
</paragraph>
